{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_03_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 渚のスケジュール",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_evening",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、どうしたものか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… What to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.3333333,
          "startTime": 5.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4633.3333333,
          "startTime": 5.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、何を見てるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you looking at‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？　な、渚か……いや、これは、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! Oh‚ Nagisa… well‚ er…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n月ストメンバーの今月のスケジュール、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's—\nIs that Moon Tempest’s schedule for this month?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ。見られてしまったらもうしょうがないな\nざっとでいいから、目を通してくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ no point hiding it now that you saw it already.\nHere‚ take a look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3333333999994,
          "startTime": 30.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ\n琴乃ちゃんは女性誌での撮影が多いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ okay.\nKotono-chan has a lot of photo sessions with women’s magazines.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはクールでかっこいいもんなぁ……\n同世代の女の子が憧れそうですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It fits well with Kotono-chan's image of coolness.\nGirls around her age look up to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんはお仕事の種類が豊富なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like Saki-chan is doing a lot of different work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "この間はミュージカルでしたけど\n最近はナレーションにレポーターまで……凄いな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was in that musical‚\nbut now she’s doing narration and even reporting… Wow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんは慣れないお仕事でも入念に準備をして\n丁寧にこなせるのが凄いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when the work is unfamiliar‚\nSaki-chan makes proper preparations and gets the job done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんは\nどうしてこれを私に……はっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why are you showing\nthis to me‚ {user}-san… Oh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "私のスケジュールの空きが……多い……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m the only one with lots of room in my schedule?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……そうなんだ。実は、月スト内で\n単独の仕事の本数に少し差が出てきていてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… A gap has appeared in\nindividual workload among Moon Tempest members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの長所を\nちゃんと見た上でのオファーが増えてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Offers have been coming in\nbased on the strengths of individual members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、いまだに個性の薄さに\n悩んでるんですよね、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that lack of\na strong individual personality is my weakness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "気を付けてはいるんですけど、油断すると\nついつい琴乃ちゃんに頼りがちになっちゃいますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ evening knowing this‚\nI tend to fall back on relying on Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの間で渚のMCは\n今日の琴乃ちゃんコーナー……なんて認識みたいだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans have started to treat your on-stage banter\nas the “Today’s Report on Kotono-chan” segment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "むむ、確かに私、普段から自分のことを\nあんまり話してないような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ouch… It’s true that I don’t usually\ntalk a lot about myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "普段の生活でも琴乃ちゃんを中心に\n考えちゃうんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tend to see things from a Kotono-chan-centric perspective\neven in my everyday life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "MCだけじゃなくて、歌やダンスでも琴乃ちゃんを\n立ててるなって、毎回ライブの後に気付くんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just on-stage banter‚ the same goes for singing and dancing…\nWhen I look back on a live‚ I realize I’m always putting Kotono-chan first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "自覚はあるのか。周りを引き立てる能力は素晴らしいが\n渚自身がもっと目立ってもいいんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like you’re aware of it. It’s a great to support those around you‚\nbut you should allow yourself to stand out a little more‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "私自身が活躍したいっていう気持ちは\nもちろんあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ a part of me wants to be\nmore active too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "なんとかしなきゃいけないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Guess I have to do something about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな\nだけどこれはすぐに解決する問題でもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right.\nBut this isn’t a problem that can be solved overnight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ゆっくり考えてみてくれ\n手伝えることがあればなんでも言ってくれていいからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Take your time and put some thought into it.\nLet me know if you need anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_01-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "……はい！　ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
